- **Type:** Nest Learning Thermostat
- **Location:** Living Room
- **Metric:** temperature (°C)
- **Purpose:** Climate control and HVAC automation
- **Data:** 720 readings at 2-minute intervals (24 hours)
- **Pattern:** Day/night cycle (18-24°C)

### 💧 Humidity Monitor - Basement  
- **ID:** device-002
- **Type:** Honeywell Humidity Sensor
- **Location:** Basement
- **Metric:** humidity (%)
- **Purpose:** Moisture control and mold prevention
- **Data:** 720 readings at 2-minute intervals (24 hours)
- **Pattern:** Inverse day/night cycle (40-70%)

### 🌤️ Barometric Pressure Sensor - Rooftop
- **ID:** device-003
- **Type:** Weather Station Sensor
- **Location:** Rooftop
- **Metric:** pressure (hPa)
- **Purpose:** Weather monitoring and prediction
