## Access Points

**Frontend:** http://localhost:4200
**Backend API:** http://localhost:5297
**Database:** (localdb)\mssqllocaldb - TelemetryDb

---

## Quick Commands

**View Devices:**
```powershell
Invoke-RestMethod -Uri "http://localhost:5297/api/devices"
```

**Send Realistic Data (24 hours):**
```powershell
.\generate-realistic-data.ps1
```

**Send Live Data (Continuous):**
```powershell
.\continuous-simulator.ps1
```

**Check Database:**
```powershell
sqlcmd -S "(localdb)\mssqllocaldb" -d "TelemetryDb" -Q "SELECT * FROM Devices"
```
